\c 4
\p
\v 1 Nifeleke Israele iaby t’i Selomò mpanjaka.
\v 2 Le zao o roandria’eo: i Azarià\f + \fr 4:2 \ft Azarià: ty mahajanjiñe \+nd \nd Iehovà\nd*\+nd*\f*, ana’ i Tsadoke mpisoroñe,
\v 3 i Elikòrefe\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Elekòrefe; Tale’ ty asotry ndra hatora’e\f* naho i Akià\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Akià: rahalahi’ \+nd \nd Iehovà\nd*\+nd*\f* ana’ i Sisà\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Sisà: atrefe’ \+nd \nd Iehovà\nd*\+nd*; marbre; fanjàka\f*, mpanokitse, Iehosafate\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Iehosafate; I \+nd \nd Iehovà\nd*\+nd* ro mpanjaka\f* ana’ i Akilode\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Akilode: samake rahalahy\f*, mpamolily;
\v 4 i Benaià ana’ Iehoiada, mpifehe i valobohòkey, le mpisoroñe t’i Tsadoke naho i Abiatare;
\v 5 i Azarià ana’ i Natane, ty mpifeleke o mpiaoloo; mpisoroñe naho mpiamy mpanjakay t’i Zabode\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Zabode, Zabade: entan’ampela: natolotse\f* ana’ i Natane;
\v 6 talè’ i anjom­bay t’i Akisare\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Akisare: rahalahi: roandriañe, sabo\f*; vaho mpiaolo ty fañondrohan-kàba t’i Abdà\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Abdà: mpitoroñe, fitoroñañe\f*.
\v 7 Nanam-pifeleke folo-ro’amby t’i Selomò nifehe Israele iaby, o namahañe i mpanjakay naho i anjomba’eio. Songa namahañe volañe raik’ ami’ty taoñe.
\v 8 Zao o tahina’ iareoo: I Ben-Kore\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Ben: anake; Kore: fidada; hafotia; hirike\f* am-bohibohi’ i Efraime;
\v 9 i Ben-Dekere\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Dekere: haozarañe\f* e Makatse\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Makatse: figadoñañe; fitamàñe\f* naho e Betesemese\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Betesemese; anjomba’ i àndroy\f* naho e Elone-Bete-Khanàne\f + \fr 4:9 \ft Elone-Bete-Khanàne: akiba’ ty mafiry\f*;
\v 10 i Ben-Kesede\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Ben-Kesede: Anam-patarihañe\f* e Arobote\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Arobote; lafinety: lalankede\f*; aze ka t’i Sokò\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Sokò: kibohotse\f* naho ze hene tane e Kefere\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Kefere: mpihaly\f*;
\v 11 i Ben’ abinadabe\f + \fr 4:11 \ft Abinadabe: raem-pañina,-pavitrihañe\f* amy fari’ i Dore\f + \fr 4:11 \ft Dore: tariratse raike, fimoneñañe\f*, aze t’i Tafate\f + \fr 4:11 \ft Tafate: evoñe mitsopake\f* anak’ ampela’ i Selomò tañanjomba’e.
\v 12 I Baana\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Baanà: ami’ty vale’e; an-kasotriañe\f*, ana’ i Akilode, aze t’i Taanake\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Taanake: i mampirek’azoy, manoiñe azo\f*, i Megi­dò\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Megidò: fanjaka o voa’eo; mitsey\f* naho i Beteseane\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Beteseane: anjomban-tsifa;\f* iaby marine’ i Tsare­tane ambane’ Iizreèle boake Beteseane pak’ Abel-mekolà\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Abel-mekolà: golobom-pitsinjahañe\f* mb’an-kalo’ Iok­neame\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Iokneame: mampionjoñe ondatio\f* ao;
\v 13 i Ben-Gebere\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Ben-Gebere: Ana-dahilahy/maozatse\f*, e Ramote\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Ramote: ankaboa\f*-gilade\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Gilade: ty votrin-talily\f*, aze o rova’ Iaere ana’ i Menasè e Giladeo; aze ka ty fari’ i Argobe\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Argobe: tane kobokara\f* e Basane\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Basane: aman-tsifa\f* ao, rova enempolo jabajaba reketse kijoly naho sikadañe torisike;
\v 14 i Akinadabe\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Akinadabe: rahalahy pañina mahimbañe\f*, ana’ Idò\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Idò: o mpirimboñe ama’eo; ozatse; enge\f*, e Maknaime\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Maknaime: Kivoho: teteke/rimboñe roe\f*;
\v 15 i Akimatse\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Akimatse: rahalahy ty fivory;\f* e Naftalý ao; nengae’e ka t’i Basmate\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Basmate: nanoañe rano mañitse; \f*, anak’ ampela’ i Selomò,
\v 16 i Ba’ anà\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Ba’anà: ami’ty navale’e; an-kasotriañe\f*, ana’ i Kosàý\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Kosày: ty falisa’ iareo; ty fianjiña’ iareo\f*, e Asere\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Asere: hafaleañe\f* naho e Bealote\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Bealone: nahifik’ ambane\f*;
\v 17 Iehosafate, ana’ i Paroà\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Paroà: miraorao; mihelañe añe\f* e Isakare;
\v 18 i Simeý\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Simeý: mahajanjiñe mañorike; engeko; \f* ana’ i Elà\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Elà: kobaiñe; fatse; fandañirañe\f*, e Beniamine;
\v 19 i Gebere\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Gebere: Vata’e lahilahy; maozatse\f* ana’ i Orý\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Orý: ty failoko; ty afoko\f*, an-tane’ i Gilade, an-tane’ i Sikone\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Sikone: Ombotañe; figadoñañe\f* mpanjaka’ o nte-Amoreo, naho a i Oge\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Og: mofo vonga’e natono am-bain’afo\f* mpanjaka’ i Basane; vaho raike ty mpifehe i tane iabiy.
\p
\v 20 Nitozantozañe mira amo faseñe añ’ olon-driakeo t’Iehoda naho Israele ami’ty hamaro’e, nikama, ninoñe vaho nifale.